 The Sex Pro mobile application (app) being tested facilitates home HIV-testing, home sexually transmitted infection (STI) test self-collection, and pre-exposure prophylaxis (PrEP) uptake.

 The app integrates a personalized HIV risk assessment with home HIV and STI testing options for young, Black MSM.

